                <h3 class="ui blue header"><u><i class="lock icon"></i>Lockers</u></h3>
                <p>Lockers are provided for the use of members and their guests but may not be used overnight.</p>

                <p>Members who do so are liable to find that the lockers are opened and locker contents removed.</p>

                <p>Removal of such items is strictly at the members own risk.</p>

                <p>Padlocks may be purchased at reception.</p>

                <p>In the interest of safety and security please use the lockers provided.</p>

                <p>The club will have no liability for goods taken from the changing rooms or lockers.</p>
            </div>
